snippet.title: Fear the Moon - Announcement Trailer [Werewolf Horror Game]
snippet.description:
Steampage now live! [ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2849730/Fear_the_Moon/ ]
"A cryptid survival horror game taking place in an Ohio forest, about a werewolf creature named "the Wolfman". Play as Jane along with her three friends who unknowingly camp the night in the Wolfman's territory deep in the forest on a long abandoned property that holds dark secrets."
